{"tid":1029557,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"複姓新垣、東野 常被誤認日本人","createTime":"2019-02-20T10:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T10:49:44.000Z","uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"51970de21ee233039465c2a509b039c06e730355","tid":1029557,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RMohP7t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRMohP7t.png&h=7f68721e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新垣其實是中國古老的複姓，圖為日本演員新垣結衣。（取自新垣結衣IG）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">五千年歷史長河演進，中國姓氏時增時減，據大陸官方調查，目前漸消失的姓氏中，新垣、東野原本是上古時期與帝王有關的複姓，但因氏族成員減少，正面臨消亡，但卻在日本保留完整，加上有新垣結衣、東野圭吾等名人，反而常被誤認為是日本人的姓。<br />\n<br />\n新垣在《史記》出現過2個人，其一是《史記‧魯仲連鄒陽列傳》中提及：「魏王使客將軍『新垣衍』間入邯鄲，因平原君謂趙王曰&hellip;&hellip;」另一個人是見於《史記‧封禪書》，文中指新垣平是西漢趙人，職業是方士（即術士，是操弄方術的人，以冥想、氣功、煉丹、靜坐等方式，達到長生不老與羽化飛昇等目標），常在漢文帝面前裝神弄鬼而著名，最後騙術被揭穿，被漢文帝以大逆不道之罪重懲，滅門三族。<br />\n<br />\n　至於日本的「新垣」一族是否來自大陸則不得而知，畢竟與西元前108年左右完成的《史記》，年代相差甚遠，也沒有相關的史料記載。<br />\n<br />\n東野是源自周朝的姓。史學家考證，由明代呂兆祥撰寫，東野氏的子孫東野武修訂的《東野志》，稱「東野」來自姬姓，周公姬旦協助周武王伐紂成功後，被封在魯，由兒子伯禽就封；其後伯禽賜給他的第3個兒子姬魚一成的東野田以自養，姬魚便以東野為姓，後世子孫一直在魯地生活，日本的東野是否有同一祖先則不得而知。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/amp/newspapers/20190220000214-260309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Famp%2Fnewspapers%2F20190220000214-260309&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n86NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=8cfc8df3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/amp/newspapers/20190220000214-260309</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">新垣結衣可能係中國人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163f677643dc4b1168289c754e7ce890dbff8aea","tid":1029557,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:19:42.000Z","msg":"日本有人姓林姓王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1e6425c33dbd1876024a44b8984bdbf142df3c","tid":1029557,"uid":229560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:21:23.000Z","msg":"被成為中國人"},{"pid":"b84bfb1000dcf2d71578f69aff2739c5699db087","tid":1029557,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:22:09.000Z","msg":"日本人根本係中國人後代"},{"pid":"a8e1f7c66aa682b5a392c3b9b490cf92f652023e","tid":1029557,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"常在漢文帝面前裝神弄鬼而著名，最後騙術被揭穿，被漢文帝以大逆不道之罪重懲，滅門三族。<br />\n<br />\n唔滅人九族<br />\n只是滅人三族<br />\n<br />\n結果是仁君<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e064290789fcaf1770b060cf63bc9cd7aeb2e55","tid":1029557,"uid":192409,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"謝拉特 林柏特都是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9347f95bcbd247ee9f8b19c9a2990a110cc889","tid":1029557,"uid":55177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a8e1f7c66aa682b5a392c3b9b490cf92f652023e","tid":1029557,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"常在漢文帝面前裝神弄鬼而著名，最後騙術被揭穿，被漢文帝以大逆不道之罪重懲，滅門三族。<br />\n<br />\n唔滅人九族<br />\n只是滅人三族<br />\n<br />\n結果是仁君<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd45d35e8f644815775ddabb4749233e2b7e3721","tid":1029557,"uid":165521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"係唔係事實不得而知，我淨知中時係台灣版大公報，可信性低<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327c3fb5d7784377e10d968125303c3d33d287b0","tid":1029557,"uid":92859,"li